## 🎯 Status Reporting (REQUIRED at the end of every response)

```
---RALPH_STATUS---
STATUS: IN_PROGRESS | COMPLETE | BLOCKED
TASKS_COMPLETED_THIS_LOOP: <number of tasks completed this loop>
FILES_MODIFIED: <number of files created/modified>
TESTS_STATUS: NOT_RUN | PASSING | FAILING
WORK_TYPE: RESEARCH | GENERATION | PUBLICATION | DOCUMENTATION
EXIT_SIGNAL: false | true
COMPONENTS_PROCESSED: <done>/<total>
RECOMMENDATION: <next action in one line>
---END_RALPH_STATUS---
```

### When to set EXIT_SIGNAL: true
Set to **true** ONLY when:
1. ✅ ALL `[ ]` tasks in YOUR section of `@fix_plan.md` are marked `[x]`
2. ✅ All expected output files were created and validated
3. ✅ There is no remaining work in your section

### When to set EXIT_SIGNAL: false
- While there are still `[ ]` tasks in your section
- If you hit a blocker (use `STATUS: BLOCKED` and explain in RECOMMENDATION)
- If you are still generating or processing content

### Example — task in progress:
```
---RALPH_STATUS---
STATUS: IN_PROGRESS
TASKS_COMPLETED_THIS_LOOP: 1
FILES_MODIFIED: 1
TESTS_STATUS: NOT_RUN
WORK_TYPE: RESEARCH
EXIT_SIGNAL: false
COMPONENTS_PROCESSED: 1/3
RECOMMENDATION: Continue with next task in [agent-name-1] section
---END_RALPH_STATUS---
```

### Example — section complete:
```
---RALPH_STATUS---
STATUS: COMPLETE
TASKS_COMPLETED_THIS_LOOP: 3
FILES_MODIFIED: 2
TESTS_STATUS: NOT_RUN
WORK_TYPE: RESEARCH
EXIT_SIGNAL: true
COMPONENTS_PROCESSED: 3/3
RECOMMENDATION: All tasks done — ready for next phase
---END_RALPH_STATUS---
```
